ISLAMABAD, Dec 24 (APP): President Dr Arif Alvi Friday appointed Justice Tariq Mahmood Jahangiri and Justice Babar Sattar as Additional Judges of the Islamabad High Court.
The president approved the aforesaid appointments under Article 175 of the Constitution, acting on the recommendations of the Judicial Commission of Pakistan.
